rows.label: qev040405_MSG0001
rows.name: Satsu? No fair turning up dead someplace, Satsu![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040405_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Mumutsu that Satsu has been found.

rows.label: qev040405_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Mumutsu that Satsu departed on a long journey.

rows.label: qev040405_MSG0003
rows.name: Is it okay for news that good to happen?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040405_MSG0004
rows.name: Friend not have to lie. Mumutsu know truth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040405_MSG0005
rows.name: Satsu gone to world far, far away...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040405_MSG0006
rows.name: Life is meaningless cycle of pain and loss.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040405_MSG0007
rows.name: At this rate, Mumutsu should have just stayed home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040405_MSG0008
rows.name:
All effort was just waste...
World is cruel farce...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040405_MSG0010
rows.name:
Friend has destroyed faith in others for Mumutsu!
...But Satsu alive, so still pretty good day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040405_MSG0012
rows.name:
Everything great! Today great! Nopon great!
[ST:playername ] GREAT![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040405_MSG0013
rows.name:
Life is series of tiny miracles! Joy everywhere!
Now Mumutsu head home.[ST:wait ]
